 So, I got comments, okay, you have Ferrari here, but no, not everybody should have Ferrari.

409
00:39:39,000 --> 00:39:44,000
 So, that's comments which I had, for example, with the discussion.

410
00:39:44,000 --> 00:39:54,000
 So, sometimes, of course, we do not have to cover macroeconomy, etc., banking sector, discussing with Polish investors.

411
